// Accordion
// Collapsible sections with three style variants (default, flush, outlined).
// Only one section is open at a time by default; supports multi-open via prop.

FUNCTION getVariantClasses(variant) -> string
  Returns Tailwind border/background classes for the given variant (default/flush/outlined).

---

FUNCTION handleToggle(sectionId)
  IF multi-open is disabled, closes the previously open section.
  Toggles the open state for the clicked section.

---

FUNCTION AccordionContent(props) -> ReactNode
  Renders the content area for an open section with an animated expand/collapse transition.

---

FUNCTION Accordion(props) -> ReactNode                                    EXPORT
  Renders a list of accordion sections, each with a header button and collapsible content.
  Applies variant-specific styling via getVariantClasses.
  Calls handleToggle when a section header is clicked.
